solPicker.job
Class Configuration

java.lang.Object
  solPicker.job.Configuration

public class Configuration
extends java.lang.Object

The configuration object keeps track of different configurations of filters to be applied to the oligos. Each configuration has a unique identification number, which is how it is later accessed by the solPicker.job, as well as filter objects.
